{"tid":1575831,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"要決定應對政府對話平台策略！","createTime":"2019-09-17T03:46:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T05:28:59.000Z","uid":128430,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cb5b78d76c3e7ffa4e2f80b2095d42627cd7779b","tid":1575831,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:46:53.000Z","msg":"反修訂《逃犯條例》風波未平，特首林鄭月娥月初提出4項行動，其中包括走進社區與市民對話。林鄭月娥今（17日）表示，首場社區對話將於下周舉行，人數約100至200，而對話亦會以3種形式同步進行。<br />\n<br />\n第一種對話會會在不同地區舉辦，市民可自由報名參加，每場約100至200人，若太多人報名，將以抽籤形式處理，對話亦會盡量公開，讓傳媒採訪<br />\n<br />\n她續稱，過往落區會有人「動員等她」，即使直接對話會引起同樣場面，她和同事也有足夠心理準備。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">自由報名果啲係公開，電視直播的，我地要考慮下係冧友報名，定係等啲藍絲廢老去哂壟斷大氣電波發言，然後政府spin到係沉默大多數。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">除左冧友，人地都邀請得我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪應該號召手足係每一場外招呼下柒婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n睇下手足點睇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"f25845dc0b52cde499299c2a0f281e11c521b5e7","tid":1575831,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:47:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"00bbd7c0a5648ff9c4ade835238ce310e66d896b","tid":1575831,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:47:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e219f24245a05f414a17e2cf1fa0cd38518d628f","tid":1575831,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:47:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"